Natural language.

233
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:40,040
And the system could automatically surface draft payroll forms and I9 verifications to submit, uh policies to review, people to connect with, and so on.

234
00:23:40,040 --> 00:23:58,520
So the promise is real, but it's still for now very much a calculated risk because agent interoperability, reliability, and data access are just not mature enough at the moment to make that experience work seamlessly at scale.

235
00:23:58,520 --> 00:24:01,800
So that's something to keep in mind here.

