This is our test of how many are still with us.

295
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:18,680
We also love to get your input.

296
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:20,040
Um, so let us know.

297
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:23,480
Do you feel like your HR team is not ready at all?

298
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:25,480
Are you not sure about your readiness?

299
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:27,400
You're like, yes, I'm ready, I've got this.

300
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:29,960
We're so ready to go where we're headed.

301
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:37,480
Um, let us know where you are.

302
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:41,560
All right, I see the numbers are coming in.

303
