There is a spectrum of agency uh for AI and HR.

501
00:50:41,840 --> 00:50:49,840
And on the left hand side, you have the the classic chat GPT experience, the rigid, reactive, static ping pong.

502
00:50:49,840 --> 00:50:52,160
