00:53:16,560 --> 00:53:43,200
The catch 22 of agentic AI in HR right now is fundamentally a piece of technology that is designed to be probabilistic in nature, because it's chances and percentage of response to a function that has always been on a more deterministic side of the house mean that we're policy question wrong, because the aftermath of that is a little HR department.

